audit/*.md

# Test coverage
coverage/

# Layer 5 test pipeline — runner bookkeeping (keep tests/<TM##>/scorecard*.md tracked)
tests/**/.preflight-*.json
tests/**/.postflight-*.json
tests/**/.invariant-drift-*.json
tests/**/triage-*.json
tests/aggregate-scorecard-*.md
tests/manual-checks-*.md
